    <p>Your browser or device may include &ldquo;Do Not Track&rdquo; functionality. artnet&rsquo;s information collection and disclosure practices, and the choices that we provide to customers, will continue to operate as described in this Privacy Policy, whether or not a &ldquo;Do Not Track&rdquo; signal is received.</p>
    <p><strong>For more information on how to control or limit cookies and similar technologies, please see <a href="http://www.allaboutcookies.org/cookies">www.allaboutcookies.org/cookies</a>.</strong></p>

    <h3>HOW WE SHARE YOUR INFORMATION</h3>

    <p>artnet shares your personal data with third parties only in the ways that are described in this Privacy Policy. artnet does not sell, rent, or lease your personal data to third parties, and artnet does not transfer your personal data to third parties for their direct marketing purposes.</p>
